  "texts": [
    "Study also states that the proposed architecture can be integrated with other neural networks at a low parameter cost.",
    "The proposed model is fully trainable, and lightweight architectire.",
    "The model will learn all the operations for extracting audio features starting from filtering to pooling steps.",
    "Based on this research [55], a new efficient, hybrid, and lightweight model can be developed which can provide high and accurate learning rate in helping the fire alarms and other audio signal detection methods.From the above survey of various former proposals and experiments that have been presented in the classification of audio files, it can be seen that the authors have included only a few models for the categorization process.",
    "However, in our research, we have included a total of seven classification models that are used in two different audio datasets having different feature extraction steps."
  ]
}